data.description: If you are looking for a beautiful house on a larger lot in Grove Pointe, this is the one for you! Located within walking distance of the park & pool, you'll always have something fun to do.  This house has well maintained hardwood floors & tile in the spacious kitchen & bathrooms.  Enjoy your fenced in back yard & enjoy grilling out while relaxing in the shade of your covered patio & mature pecan trees!  Located in Hahira, but close to everything and everywhere you need to go in the amazing & growing city of Valdosta!
